OL,3,CCost of diesel rises by 50p on the
OL,4,CIsle of Man
OL,6,FThe price of diesel on the Isle of Man
OL,7,Fhas increased by 50p after some pumps
OL,8,Fran dry as drivers are urged not to
OL,9,Fpanic buy or stockpile fuel.
OL,11,FPrices across the island average at
OL,12,F185.9p per litre, with queues forming
OL,13,Fat various petrol stations.
OL,15,FA number of diesel pumps on the island
OL,16,Fran dry over the weekend, with one
OL,17,Fsupplier asking residents to "avoid
OL,18,Frefilling" until a fresh supply
OL,19,Farrived to the island.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
