OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774951543
OL,3,CCost of diesel rises by 50p on the
OL,4,CIsle of Man
OL,6,FOther businesses decided to limit
OL,7,Fcustomers to a maximum of #20, as
OL,8,Fdrivers responded to worries over the
OL,9,Fongoing conflict in the Middle East.
OL,11,FAn oil tanker was due to arrive in
OL,12,FPeel on 27 March, but had to shelter
OL,13,Ffrom the bad weather off of Port
OL,14,FSoderick over the weekend.
OL,16,FA fresh supply of diesel was delivered
OL,17,Fto the island on Monday 30 March.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
