OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774951543
OL,3,CCost of diesel rises by 50p on the
OL,4,CIsle of Man
OL,6,FThe Chief Minister warned the Island
OL,7,Fwould see 'significant' increases due
OL,8,Fto the ongoing conflict in the Middle
OL,9,FEast.
OL,11,FAlfred Cannan will be asked again in
OL,12,Fthe House of Keys on Tuesday whether
OL,13,Fany further contingnency plans are in
OL,14,Fplace to tackle future shortages.
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
